data.description: PRICE REDUCTION to make it even more accessible for those who dream of living in this exclusive neighborhood. No need to wait for new construction! Embrace the quality of life Brunswick Crossing has to offer! Amenity rich with pocket playgrounds throughout, 26 miles of walking paths, a community center, gym, pool, tennis and volleyball ball courts, community garden and activities galore. Nearby shopping and restaurants. This is a must SEE!  Beautiful 4 bed 4 bath  Colonial  with spacious open floor plan.  From the Gourmet Kitchen to the master suite with a gorgeous super bath to the balcony to the movie theater this home has everything you need! Huge lower level with full bath and walk out providing  easy access to hit the paved nature trails throughout the community or head to the pool. 4 bedrooms on the upper level giving plenty of space.  You don't want to miss this beauty! Imagine waking up every morning and enjoying a hot cup of coffee on your balcony!
